    <summary>Determines when changes to a data source value get propagated to the corresponding data-bound control property.</summary>
    <remarks>
      <format type="text/markdown"><![CDATA[  
  
## Remarks  
 The <xref:System.Windows.Forms.ControlUpdateMode> is used by the <xref:System.Windows.Forms.Binding.ControlUpdateMode%2A> property of the <xref:System.Windows.Forms.Binding> class. OnPropertyChanged is the default value. To force a control update when the update mode is Never, use the <xref:System.Windows.Forms.Binding.ReadValue%2A> method on the related <xref:System.Windows.Forms.Binding>.  
  
 ]]></format>
    </remarks>
